Application.html.title: Application
Application.html.name: Application
Application.html.description: Application Class for use to define an application.An application contains metadata and initializers for the application.Applications track history, and normally would contain the entire single page App startup. Supported options are: metadata - an object of metadata to use for storing propertiesname - the name of the applicationdatastore - a datastore to use via the datastore propertyrouter - the router to use via the router property
